data.description: Stunning 4bed/3.5bath home with great views on double cul­-de-­sac on private greenbelt in Boerne. Offering wood floors on main level, huge island and granite in kitchen with tons of cabinetry and views of the greenbelt make this home move­-in ready. The main floor, large master suite provides a bay window, tray ceiling, and mud-­set shower. Welcoming you outdoors is a cedar deck, stained covered patio, and custom landscaping. Boerne ISD schools, convenient access to I­10, and No City Tax.
